{"tid":463387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港對巴林開賽前播中國國歌 球迷照噓高呼「We are Hong Kong」","createTime":"2017-11-09T12:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T12:37:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"59635a57bd01ec440e168a62bdb90fa37921f2ab","tid":463387,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171109/large/1510229414_82bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F1510229414_82bc.jpg&h=20e51974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角大球場今晚8時進行香港對巴林足球友誼賽。今次是全國人大常委會上周六（4日）通過將《國歌法》納入香港《基本法》附件三後，港足首場迎戰外國球隊的球賽。<br />\n<br />\n球賽開始前先播放巴林國歌，完結後獲球迷鼓掌；隨後主持表示將播放中國國歌，現場球迷即時起哄狂噓，一直噓至國歌播放完畢，更有不少球迷沒有站立，無懼《國歌法》的「緊箍咒」。眾人未待國歌完結，已開始擊鼓，國歌法一完結即大叫「We are Hong Kong」，當中夾雜「收皮」及其他粗言穢語，打氣聲則延至球賽開始。<br />\n場內球迷區及非球迷區均有便衣警員駐守，但未有對噓國歌人士作任何行動。工作人員則阻止在場人士攝錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57439021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57439021&d=u2V4FAe0VNi%2BBpfrTfl2yBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=ff853875\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57439021&h=f02e058b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57439021</a>"},{"pid":"0a55556785eb5aee7e5872f861d3b3cde6f5e06d","tid":463387,"uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171109/large/1510229587_6784.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F1510229587_6784.jpg&h=86428067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n球場內有疑似便衣警員戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171109/large/1510229591_ce34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F1510229591_ce34.jpg&h=8df50702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看台上亦有零星人士高舉中國國旗。"},{"pid":"419747aad1f47c7ccdcf26f34a96c916158c6875","tid":463387,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"開咁多個陣間五毛屌你洗皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b975dc29abe7e7b03981600e33787c86c1fe68","tid":463387,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"俾掌聲巴林國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e4ee0151c04347e1e15cc36c12beca967bf2f6","tid":463387,"uid":84830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"噓左又唔係罰啲球迷，噓未噓囉，on99"},{"pid":"a741c9cc82453293972b3bab992cecb4c9d68b98","tid":463387,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9196701c3920e58f787a18f31549229ac36ec8","tid":463387,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"各大民主牆寫hong kong is not china<br />\n然後啲中國學生就會好嬲加but belongs to"}]}